query:
INSERT INTO course_background_questions (
    id,
    course_id,
    course_instance_id,
    question_text,
    question_type
  )
SELECT uuid_generate_v5($1, id::text),
  $1,
  uuid_generate_v5($1, course_instance_id::text),
  question_text,
  question_type
FROM course_background_questions
WHERE course_id = $2
  AND deleted_at IS NULL;
